#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jve.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.jve"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:1 of
msgid "Exponentially scaled Bessel function of the first kind of order `v`."
msgstr "指数缩放的第一类贝塞尔函数，阶数为 `v`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:3 of
msgid "Defined as::"
msgstr "定义如下："

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jve.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:7 of
msgid "Order (float)."
msgstr "阶数（浮点数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:9 of
msgid "Argument (float or complex)."
msgstr "自变量（浮点数或复数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:11 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jve.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:14 of
msgid "**J** -- Value of the exponentially scaled Bessel function."
msgstr "**J** —— 指数缩放贝塞尔函数的值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jve.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`jv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:20 of
msgid "Unscaled Bessel function of the first kind"
msgstr "未缩放的第一类贝塞尔函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:23 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:24 of
msgid ""
"For positive `v` values, the computation is carried out using the AMOS "
"[1]_ `zbesj` routine, which exploits the connection to the modified "
"Bessel function :math:`I_v`,"
msgstr ""
"对于正的 `v` 值，使用 AMOS [1]_ 的 `zbesj` 程序进行计算，该程序利用了与"
"修正贝塞尔函数 :math:`I_v` 的关系，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:28 of
msgid ""
"J_v(z) = \\exp(v\\pi\\imath/2) I_v(-\\imath z)\\qquad (\\Im z > 0)\n"
"\n"
"J_v(z) = \\exp(-v\\pi\\imath/2) I_v(\\imath z)\\qquad (\\Im z < 0)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:33 of
msgid "For negative `v` values the formula,"
msgstr "对于负的 `v` 值，使用公式，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:35 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"J_{-v}(z) = J_v(z) \\cos(\\pi v) - Y_v(z) \\sin(\\pi v)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:37 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`Y_v(z)` is the Bessel function of the second kind, "
"computed using the AMOS routine `zbesy`.  Note that the second term is "
"exactly zero for integer `v`; to improve accuracy the second term is "
"explicitly omitted for `v` values such that `v = floor(v)`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`Y_v(z)` 是第二类贝塞尔函数，使用 AMOS 程序 `zbesy` 计算。请"
"注意，当 `v` 为整数时第二项严格为零；为了提高精度，当 `v = floor(v)` 时"
"显式省略第二项。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:42 of
msgid ""
"Exponentially scaled Bessel functions are useful for large arguments `z`:"
" for these, the unscaled Bessel functions can easily under-or overflow."
msgstr ""
"指数缩放的贝塞尔函数对大自变量 `z` 很有用：对于这些情况，未缩放的贝塞尔"
"函数很容易发生下溢或上溢。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:46 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jve:47 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, 一个用于复数自变量和非负阶数贝塞尔函数的便携式"
"程序包\", http://netlib.org/amos/"

